NAME
       togif - convert an IRIS image to a Compuserve GIF image

SYNOPSIS
       togif inimage.rgb outimage.gif

DESCRIPTION
       togif  converts  an  IRIS image file to a Compuserve GIF
       image file format.

SEE ALSO
       fromgif(6D)
